LAY LA <br />\n個個站都仲圍哂板</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mtr-shatincentrallink.hk/tc/construction/related-work.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr-shatincentrallink.hk%2Ftc%2Fconstruction%2Frelated-work.html&d=ciygD08X6SLTudZy%2FuUlmTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=4c9d882f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr-shatincentrallink.hk/tc/construction/related-work.html</a><br />\n月台加固???? 4月仲砌緊磚姐係未做好啦</blockquote><br />\n1 delay 影響冇咁大<br />\n未砌好磚但係新信號試新車都可以同步呀嘛</blockquote><br />\n你細心d 睇 1尾係接4頭 <br />\n咁唔一定全條線做哂 可以一個個站嘅</blockquote><br />\n你見到邊度砌磚"},{"pid":"2d349f62773ecb0de9486127c24423db497c0dac","tid":279052,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:07:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68dbbec5abb1deb0c73007f510b528244781d554","tid":279052,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:27:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n新信號系統delay--&gt;新車遲落地行--&gt;英製列車遲退--&gt;幕門要遲裝<br />\n環環相扣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪戇鳩1. 都DELAY LA <br />\n個個站都仲圍哂板</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mtr-shatincentrallink.hk/tc/construction/related-work.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr-shatincentrallink.hk%2Ftc%2Fconstruction%2Frelated-work.html&d=ciygD08X6SLTudZy%2FuUlmTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=4c9d882f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr-shatincentrallink.hk/tc/construction/related-work.html</a><br />\n月台加固???? 4月仲砌緊磚姐係未做好啦</blockquote><br />\n1 delay 影響冇咁大<br />\n未砌好磚但係新信號試新車都可以同步呀嘛</blockquote><br />\n你細心d 睇 1尾係接4頭 <br />\n咁唔一定全條線做哂 可以一個個站嘅</blockquote><br />\n你見到邊度砌磚</blockquote><br />\n你出多D街唔好成日對住電腦就見到</blockquote><br />\n問下咩站使唔使咁惡<br />\n我返工又唔係東鐵嗰頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時間唔中搭都唔見有啲位未砌好"},{"pid":"11fe2deb48d768efa8d7c67f40405093f2c5c0d1","tid":279052,"uid":7165